{"id":148,"parent_id":121,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":148,"title":"Numbers 27","subtitle":"","short_title":"Num.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/27","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 27"],[".studySummary",["i","The law of inheritances to sons, daughters, and kinsmen is explained—Moses will see but not enter the promised land—Joshua is called and set apart to lead Israel."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/27.1","order":"02.05.027.13326"},["b","1"],"Then came the daughters of Zelophehad, the son of Hepher, the son of Gilead, the son of Machir, the son of Manasseh, of the families of Manasseh the son of Joseph: and these",["i","are"],"the names of his daughters; Mahlah, Noah, and Hoglah, and Milcah, and Tirzah."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/27.2","order":"02.05.027.13327"},["b","2"],"And they stood before Moses, and before Eleazar the priest, and before the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"princes"],"and all the congregation,",["i","by"],"the door of the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"tabernacle of the congregation"],", saying,"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/27.3","order":"02.05.027.13328"},["b","3"],"Our father died in the wilderness, and he was not in the company of them that gathered themselves together against the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"in the company of Korah; but died in his own sin, and had no sons."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/27.4","order":"02.05.027.13329"},["b","4"],"Why should the name of our father be done away from among his family, because he hath no son? Give unto us",["i","therefore"],"a possession among the brethren of our father."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/27.5","order":"02.05.027.13330"},["b","5"],"And Moses brought their cause before the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/27.6","order":"02.05.027.13331"},["b","6"],"¶And the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"spake unto Moses, saying,"],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/27.7","order":"02.05.027.13332"},["b","7"],"The daughters of Zelophehad speak right: thou shalt surely give them a possession of an",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"inheritance"],"among their father’s brethren; and thou shalt cause the inheritance of their father to pass unto them."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/27.8","order":"02.05.027.13333"},["b","8"],"And thou shalt speak unto the children of Israel, saying, If a man die, and have no son, then ye shall cause his inheritance to pass unto his daughter."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/27.9","order":"02.05.027.13334"},["b","9"],"And if he have no daughter, then ye shall give his inheritance unto his brethren."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/27.10","order":"02.05.027.13335"},["b","10"],"And if he have no brethren, then ye shall give his inheritance unto his father’s brethren."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/27.11","order":"02.05.027.13336"},["b","11"],"And if his father have no brethren, then ye shall give his inheritance unto his kinsman that is next to him of his family, and he shall possess it: and it shall be unto the children of Israel a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"statute of judgment"],", as the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"commanded Moses."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/27.12","order":"02.05.027.13337"},["b","12"],"¶And the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"said unto Moses, Get thee up into this mount",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"Abarim"],", and see the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"land"],"which I have given unto the children of Israel."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/27.13","order":"02.05.027.13338"},["b","13"],"And when thou hast seen it, thou also shalt be gathered unto thy people, as Aaron thy brother was gathered."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/27.14","order":"02.05.027.13339"},["b","14"],"For ye rebelled against my commandment in the desert of Zin, in the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"strife"],"of the congregation, to sanctify me at the water before their eyes: that",["i","is"],"the water of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"Meribah"],"in",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_14c"},"Kadesh"],"in the wilderness of Zin."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/27.15","order":"02.05.027.13340"},["b","15"],"¶And Moses spake unto the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", saying,"],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/27.16","order":"02.05.027.13341"},["b","16"],"Let the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"God"],"of the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"spirits"],"of all flesh,",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_16c"},"set"],"a man over the congregation,"],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/27.17","order":"02.05.027.13342"},["b","17"],"Which may go out before them, and which may go in before them, and which may lead them out, and which may bring them in; that the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"congregation"],"of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"be not as",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"sheep"],"which have no",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_17c"},"shepherd"],"."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/27.18","order":"02.05.027.13343"},["b","18"],"¶And the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"said unto Moses, Take thee",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"Joshua"],"the son of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"Nun"],", a man in whom",["i","is"],"the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_18c"},"spirit"],", and",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_18d"},"lay"],"thine hand upon him;"],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/27.19","order":"02.05.027.13344"},["b","19"],"And",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"set"],"him before Eleazar the priest, and before all the congregation; and give him a charge in their sight."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/27.20","order":"02.05.027.13345"},["b","20"],"And thou shalt",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"put"],["i","some"],"of thine",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_20b"},"honour"],"upon him, that all the congregation of the children of Israel may be obedient."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/27.21","order":"02.05.027.13346"},["b","21"],"And he shall stand before Eleazar the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"priest"],", who shall ask",["i",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_21b"},"counsel"]],"for him",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_21c"},"after"],"the judgment of",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_21d"},"Urim"],"before the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],": at his word shall they go out, and at his word they shall come in,",["i","both"],"he, and all the children of Israel with him, even all the congregation."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/27.22","order":"02.05.027.13347"},["b","22"],"And Moses did as the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"commanded him: and he took Joshua, and set him before Eleazar the priest, and before all the congregation:"],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/27.23","order":"02.05.027.13348"},["b","23"],"And he",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"laid"],"his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_23b"},"hands"],"upon him, and gave him a",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_23c"},"charge"],", as the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"commanded by the hand of Moses."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/27.2a","order":"02.05.027.13349"},["b","2a"],["span.small","HEB"],"leaders, rulers."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/27.2b","order":"02.05.027.13351"},["b","2b"],["span.small","HEB"],"tent of meeting."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/27.7a","order":"02.05.027.13353"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/36.2.1-13"},"Num. 36:2 (1–13)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/josh/17.4"},"Josh. 17:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/27.11a","order":"02.05.027.13355"},["b","11a"],["span.small","HEB"],"statutory law."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/27.12a","order":"02.05.027.13357"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/32.49.48-52"},"Deut. 32:49 (48–52)"],"."],["div",{"id":"12b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/27.12b","order":"02.05.027.13359"},["b","12b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/promised-lands"},"TG Promised Lands"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/27.14a","order":"02.05.027.13361"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/strife"},"TG Strife"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/27.14b","order":"02.05.027.13363"},["b","14b"],["span.small","HEB"],"Contention."],["div",{"id":"14c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/27.14c","order":"02.05.027.13365"},["b","14c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/20.1.1-29"},"Num. 20:1 (1–29)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/32.51.48-52"},"Deut. 32:51 (48–52)"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/27.16a","order":"02.05.027.13367"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-the-father-elohim"},"TG God the Father, Elohim"],"."],["div",{"id":"16b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/27.16b","order":"02.05.027.13369"},["b","16b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/man-antemortal-existence-of"},"TG Man, Antemortal Existence of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/spirit-body"},"Spirit Body"],"."],["div",{"id":"16c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/27.16c","order":"02.05.027.13371"},["b","16c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/a-of-f/1.5"},"A of F 1:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/27.17a","order":"02.05.027.13373"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/church-organization"},"TG Church Organization"],"."],["div",{"id":"17b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/27.17b","order":"02.05.027.13375"},["b","17b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sheep"},"TG Sheep"],"."],["div",{"id":"17c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/27.17c","order":"02.05.027.13377"},["b","17c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/shepherd"},"TG Shepherd"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/27.18a","order":"02.05.027.13379"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/3.21"},"Deut. 3:21"],"."],["div",{"id":"18b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/27.18b","order":"02.05.027.13381"},["b","18b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.28"},"Num. 11:28"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/josh/14.1"},"Josh. 14:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"18c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/27.18c","order":"02.05.027.13383"},["b","18c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-spirit-of"},"TG God, Spirit of"],"."],["div",{"id":"18d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/27.18d","order":"02.05.027.13385"},["b","18d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/church-organization"},"TG Church Organization"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/27.19a","order":"02.05.027.13387"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/common-consent"},"TG Common Consent"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/setting-apart"},"Setting Apart"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sustaining-church-leaders"},"Sustaining Church Leaders"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/27.20a","order":"02.05.027.13389"},["b","20a"],["span.small","OR"],"invest him with some of your authority."],["div",{"id":"20b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/27.20b","order":"02.05.027.13391"},["b","20b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/delegation-of-responsibility"},"TG Delegation of Responsibility"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/27.21a","order":"02.05.027.13393"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/16.32.1-34"},"Lev. 16:32 (1–34)"],"."],["div",{"id":"21b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/27.21b","order":"02.05.027.13395"},["b","21b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/josh/9.14"},"Josh. 9:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"21c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/27.21c","order":"02.05.027.13397"},["b","21c"],["span.small","OR"],"as revealed through the Urim and Thummim."],["div",{"id":"21d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/27.21d","order":"02.05.027.13399"},["b","21d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/urim-and-thummim"},"TG Urim and Thummim"],"."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/27.23a","order":"02.05.027.13401"},["b","23a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/priesthood-ordination"},"TG Priesthood, Ordination"],"."],["div",{"id":"23b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/27.23b","order":"02.05.027.13403"},["b","23b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/hands-laying-on-of"},"TG Hands, Laying on of"],"."],["div",{"id":"23c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/27.23c","order":"02.05.027.13405"},["b","23c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/called-of-god"},"TG Called of God"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/priesthood-authority"},"Priesthood, Authority"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/priesthood-history-of"},"Priesthood, History of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/stewardship"},"Stewardship"],"."]]}
